nodes.text: The ZH-25 Questor-class, also known as the ZH-25 freighter, was a class of freighter manufactured by Starfeld Industries. When Yrica Quell visited the Entropian Hive to recruit Nath Tensent into the New Republic, she noticed a modified ZH-25 freighter fly past. The ZH-40 Tribune-class light freighter, also produced by Starfeld Industries, was a later relative of the ZH-25.
